@@ -1,5 +1,8 @@
 # Payment API
 
 `POST /payments` creates a payment charge.
 
 The current fixture intentionally does not yet document idempotency behavior. BURHAN's future documentation validator must reject this omission.
+
+Send an `Idempotency-Key` header when retrying a payment. Concurrent requests
+with the same key resolve to one charge.
